<ext_description linkend="Document_definition_mim.restrict_document_definition_category">
The <b>restrict_document_definition_category</b> rule constrains every instance of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> of type 'digital document definition' or 'physical document definition' to be a definition of a product of category 'document'.
</ext_description>

<ext_description linkend="Document_definition_mim.restrict_document_definition_category.wr:WR1">
There shall not be any instance of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> that defines a digital file or a physical document, that is not a definition of a version of a product of category 'document'.
</ext_description>
